    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Structures or other places of adode; in a legal sense, a domicile is the primary dwelling of a person, their fixed or permanent location.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
